reator><![CDATA[brooskybroosky]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Idk who needs to hear it, but this is what suicidal depression can look like</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4k7fb7Z</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dBzc3va.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Me, 5 years ago, pregnant with the Man Cub. My whole life, I looked forward to being a mom more than anything else. I was beyond ecstatic when the stick turned blue! 

But then the morning sickness turned into hyperemesis gravidarum. The (now ex) husband turned into the adulterer. The happiest time in my life turned into multiple hospital stays for physical and mental health reasons.  

I went from wanting nothing more than picking names and decorating a nursery to afraid to drive because I kept having very, very vivid fantasies of crashing my car into a guard rail. 

Parenthood is HARD. 
Pregnancy is HARD. 
Asking for help during what’s supposed to be the most magical, happy time in your life is HARD. 

For anyone who needs a soft spot to land when life is hard, I’m here. 

FP Edit. To everyone who has shared kind words -both to me & other commenters- and/or been open about their own struggles-thank you!!! The whole reason I shared this story was because I’d gone to a PPA/PPD support group at 4 weeks postpartum…and was the only. fucking. person who showed up. So not only did I feel like a horrible horrendous failure of a mom but I felt like I was the ONLY horrible horrendous failure of a mom. No one should ever feel that alone. I’m so grateful for everyone who has contributed to helping other women know how normal this is and helping them find courage to ask for help.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4k7fb7Z</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[H0llyheadHarpy]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JLRGAg0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ch8wcgf.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JLRGAg0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Small dump, четврти</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OhSHP9P</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/shIykg5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bk8QJsS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HBckWWe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KdBWewh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TlEeL21.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AlyBAj6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HHRPxAN.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;